title: #92Noon! 11a Hour 2/9 - JonnyAthletic/Vikes chat
description: Jon Krawczynski joins to open the hour on the Wolves, NBA trade deadline opinions and more...then rest of show with thoughts on Vikings news, in regard to Ryan Grigson's hire, and the steam on Ed Donatell becoming D Coordinator.
